data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning four-bedroom, three-bathroom home located in an exclusive, prestigious neighborhood. Nestled close to the renowned Belmont Country Club Golf Course on an expansive property. Enjoy a secluded courtyard, a generously proportioned family room featuring a vaulted ceiling and a cozy fireplace. Head inside to find an updated kitchen that's a chef's dream, featuring modern amenities and sleek design. Freshly painted walls and new flooring throughout the home provide a sense of freshness and modernity, enhancing the overall ambiance. The property also boasts a secure pool area, a delightful play space, and an extensive covered patio, all ideal for hosting gatherings and events. This residence is not just a house; it's a lifestyle. With its prime location, elegant updates, and a layout designed for comfort and entertainment, this home is your ticket to the upscale living you've always dreamed of. Make it yours and experience the pinnacle of comfort and prestige.
